body: "## Algorithm portfolio\n\n### Execution graph\nTopological layering; longest weighted path and slack; dominators; prerequisite frontier; transitive reduction; minimum cut candidates; resource-constrained scheduling inputs.\n\n### Impact graph\nReverse reachability; bounded personalized PageRank or diffusion; articulation and bridge analysis; fan-in or fan-out; dependency cones; affected evidence and ownership.\n\n### Knowledge graph\nWeak and strong components by kind family; Leiden or Louvain-style communities with deterministic seeds; degree, eigenvector, betweenness approximations; structural similarity; redundant and contradictory paths.\n\n### Temporal and multi-agent graph\nIncremental maintenance; snapshot deltas; edge survival and decay; change-point detection; event-time windows; merge or federation boundaries; contention hot spots.\n\n### Context selection\nGraph-distance features; spreading activation; prerequisite and evidence boosts; diversity-aware MMR or DPP-style packing; novelty and redundancy penalties; bounded anytime assembly.\n\nAll outputs must identify edge families, snapshot, exact or approximate status, limits, freshness, and why each result matters."
